      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "A damage suit for $4,000 against\nthe Great Northern was filed in the\nfederal court yesterday by Arson\nMcDermid, who alleges that while\nIn the company's employ at Troy,\nMont, May 10, the sight of one\neye was destroyed by the breaking\nof a lubricator valve. Negligence\non the part of the master mechanic\nand rounhouse foreman, who are\nalleged to have known the valve\nwas defective, Is charged.\n\n\nThe case is brought under the\nemployers liability act."
    }
